<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Saw one of these drop last night in the Hole off of a named elemental named something like Gibantik.  At first I thought it was someone's pet, then I realized we didn't have any mages with us on the raid :)   <BR>
<BR>
The mob conned yellow to me at 47.  He's a caster too, more than likely a wizzy with the damage he was dealing.  He was inside the castle-like structure not far into the hole.<BR>
